<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> jayābhyudaya śālivāhanaśakavarṣa
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ṁbbulu 1526 Agunēṭi krōdhināmasaṁvva
<lb n="3" break="no"/>tsara Āśvīja śu 10 śu <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> hajarati mahāma
<lb n="4" break="no"/>dakhullipādaśahā voḍayaluṁgāri paṁppuna
<lb n="5"/>Aśvarāyaniṁgāru kovvulavāri koṭhāmu vīragō
<lb n="6" break="no"/>ṭhāmu yaṟajerllalū sādhiṁcci mukuṁddabāhu
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ba ḷēṁdrunini sarahaddu vaḷladarimi kūrmmamu va
<lb n="8" break="no"/>cci kūrmmanāthuniki nityanaivēdyālu rāgabhōgālu taḍuvu
<lb n="9" break="no"/>lanuṁḍḍi sāgaka Uṁḍḍaṁgānu padmanāyakulu vipparlla
<lb n="10" break="no"/>gōtrulu rājādhirāja mahārāja rājaśrī kamaḷa
<lb n="11" break="no"/>yyaṁgāri putrulū sarvappa Aśvarāyaniṁgāru śrī
<lb n="12" break="no"/>kūrmmanādhuni prītigānu kūrmmagrāmamu krōdhināma
<lb n="13" break="no"/>saṁvatsara mṛgaśira sālumāḍalugānu pōlamu me
<lb n="14" break="no"/>rakapallamu palavṛkṣālu ceruvulu tōṁṭalu grāma
<lb n="15"/>Ādāyamu sarvamunnu sarvamānyamugānu śrīkū
<lb n="16" break="no"/>rmmanāthani nityanaivēdyamu dīpārādhana śēvakulaku vrittulu 21
<lb n="17"/>rāmānujakūṭamuku vrittu<unclear>r</unclear>lu tōṁṭalu pāṭakamūlamu
<lb n="18"/>śrīvaiṣṇavulaku vrittulu 21 brāhmalaku vrittulu 22 yīco
<lb n="19"/>ppuna kaṭaḍacēśi <unclear>sa</unclear>marpaṇacēśiri <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> svadattādviguṇaṁ puṇya<supplied reason="omitted">ṁ</supplied>
<lb n="20"/>paradattānupālanaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> paradattāvahārēṇa svadattaṁ niṣpalaṁ bhavēt <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
<lb n="21"/>Ēkaiva bhaginī lōkē sarvēṣāmēva bhūbhujāṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> nabhōjyā na ka
<lb n="22" break="no"/>ragrāhyā vipra(śrī dēva)dattā pasuṁdharā <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śrīśrīśrīṁ jēyunū <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied>
</p>

